description:
Get exclusive access to exciting content and our entire DVD library all while helping to support us at https://patreon.com/fountainview
Twice a year, Fountainview Academy hosts a Week of Prayer. This time of prayer and spiritual focus is always a blessing for all participating faculty and students. We hope to share our enthusiasm and love for this event through this live stream.

chapters.title: He Heard the Cry It Is Finished Announcing that the Redemption of the Lost Race Was Forever Made Certain that Heaven Was Made Eternally Secure against the Accusations the Deceptions the Pretensions that Satan Would Instigate Now Watch this beyond the Cross of Calvary with Its Agony and Shame Jesus Looked Forward to the Great Final Day When the Prince of the Power of the Air Will Meet His Destruction in the Earth So Long Marred by His Rebellion Jesus Beheld the Work of Evil Forever Ended and the Peace of God Filling Have Enter so that Fall like Lightning Includes So Far Three and I'M GonNa Say There's a Fourth One Coming Up Steps

And if You Get Just the Right Flight of Steps Right with the Just the Right You Know Angle to It the Depth of the Steps and the Tread and All this Kind of Stuff You Can Do this Amazing Thing with the Slinky You Can Get at the Very Top of that Side Five Steps and Put It Right on the Edge and if You Flip It Just Give It a Little Nudge a Little Tip Right It Won't Just Go Down to One Step As Soon as It Goes Shh

And if all God Wanted To Do Was Destroy Satan He Could Have Done It Right Then and There and Heaven Would Have Gone On and Not Missed a Beat but God Has a Bigger Plan than Merely Destroying Satan He Wants To Take Us Home Too but He Can't Just Be like All Right Let's Go Get Him Right Now Whoa Slow Down We'D Mess It Up so He Says I'M GonNa Turn those Sinners into Saints and I'M GonNa Give Them the Power Not Just the Pardon for Them but but the Power To Overcome Him by the Blood of the Land

But God Has a Bigger Plan than Merely Destroying Satan He Wants To Take Us Home Too but He Can't Just Be like All Right Let's Go Get Him Right Now Whoa Slow Down We'D Mess It Up so He Says I'M GonNa Turn those Sinners into Saints and I'M GonNa Give Them the Power Not Just the Pardon for Them but but the Power To Overcome Him by the Blood of the Land by the Word of Their Testimony

God Is Working through a Process One Step at a Time so that Two Purposes Can Be Accomplished Number One the Whole Universe We'Ll See Why It's Not Just Okay but It's Necessary To Destroy Satan and Number Two How It's GonNa Work To Bring Sinners Back Home Friends I'M Going To Tell You this Right Now I'Ve Said It Over and over the Whole Purpose of this Life Is To Figure Out if We Even Want the Next Life Do We Want To Go Live There

And I Think There's a Reason Scripture Says Things like Remember Your Creator in the Days of Your Youth because Right Now You Are Forming those Habits That Become the Lifestyle That Will Determine Your Destiny It's Called Building Character You'Ve Probably Seen It on some Signs around Here but It's a Pretty Good Tagline I Don't Have a Stirring Piece of Music To Play or some Heartfelt Appeal or an Emotional Story To Tell You I Just Want To Pet It in Plain Facts View Tonight this Life the Only Purpose Is To Make a Decision about the Next Line

I Don't Have a Stirring Piece of Music To Play or some Heartfelt Appeal or an Emotional Story To Tell You I Just Want To Pet It in Plain Facts View Tonight this Life the Only Purpose Is To Make a Decision about the Next Line and every Subset of Decision That You Make Is Contributing to that One Great Decision either for or against and I Don't Know about You but As Much as I Love God's Promise To Prepare a Place for Me I Want Him To Start Working on Me To Prepare Me for that

I Certainly Hope and Pray that each One of You Takes this Life for As Long or As Short as It May Last To Make that Decision for Eternity Let's Heavily Father Lord Tonight We See in Your Word that You Have a Plan Bigger than Merely Ending Sin but You Want To Redeem Sinners Praise the Lord for Your Mercy for Your Part That Is Freely Offered and the Power That Is Always Available for Anyone Who Wants To Be Part of Your Kingdom Lord Forgive Us When We Have Not Seen or Properly Appreciated the Inestimable Gift That You Offer Us

And Let Us by Our Own Actions Our Decisions Our Thoughts Our Characters Lord Do More than Merely Settle into a Reduced Concept of Salvation Where It's Just a Ticket at Just a Transaction To Get Money a Salvation in My Hand and I Can Live My Life no Lord Help Us To Put that Away Help Us To Have the Bigger Picture in Mind There's a Guiding Principle for the Rest of Our Lives that Our Purpose
